@startuml
title Signal Waveform Demo
concise Bus
robust State
clock clk
binary enable
@0
Bus is Idle
State is Reset
clk is high
enable is low
@5
Bus is Active
State is Running
clk is low
enable is high
@10
Bus is Idle
State is Running
clk is high
@15
Bus is Wait
State is Paused
clk is low
enable is low
@20
Bus is Idle
State is Reset
clk is high
@enduml
